{"tid":1900216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"禁入境者激增3,388人","createTime":"2020-02-27T05:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T06:19:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4c7599286ab8021f58c9d423ba8a886c08da20","tid":1900216,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200227/KQHV5UHTDDXL54VFFKEVMVQKCA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200227%2FKQHV5UHTDDXL54VFFKEVMVQKCA%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgbHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=90264bcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200227%2FKQHV5UHTDDXL54VFFKEVMVQKCA%2F&h=38f1b3f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200227/KQHV5UHTDDXL54VFFKEVMVQKCA/</a><br />\n<br />\n禁入境者激增3,388人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200227/large/1582734908_494d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200227%2Flarge%2F1582734908_494d.jpg&h=c651ac46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人權觀察執行總監羅思今年初被拒入境香港。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港入境處近幾年多次拒絕訪客入境，包括國際非政府組織「人權觀察」（Human Right Watch）執行總監羅思（Kenneth Roth）、曾經來港採訪反送中示威的美國著名戰地記者邁克爾．嚴（Michael Yon）等等，但是入境處從未就拒絕他們入境解釋原因。據入境處數字，去年比前年拒絕入境人數，比前一年增加3,388人。有人權組織認為，政府拒絕入境人數有上升趨勢，這是收緊香港出入境政策，政府極權的表現。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「政治預算案」無助挽民望<br />\n<br />\n人權組織轟極權手段<br />\n<br />\n香港入境處數字顯示，本港去年有57,583名訪客/海員被拒入境，比前年人數54,195人為多，按年增加6.25%。香港人權監察總幹事羅沃啟認為，入境處數字未能反映實際情況，「有啲人明知道會被拒絕入境就唔會嚟，呢種手段係對香港出入境政策收緊，服務大陸政治利益，針對唔同政見人士」。<br />\n<br />\n羅沃啟指出，國際非政府組織人權觀察執行總監羅思今年初被拒入境香港，「明顯係中國話反制佢哋，但香港有人權唔能夠拒絕佢哋入境」。他說：「好似香港搞論壇，冇理由人哋講咗啲嘢唔符合大陸政治利益，然後唔畀人入嚟。」中央近年干預香港越來越多，「入境處黑名單都係受制於大陸」，入境處拒絕入境實質是「極權、懼怕自由，對付正常行使文明嘅手段」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張文鈴"},{"pid":"6a80e8185524a22d4c10e5dcfbe72669ad0235cf","tid":1900216,"uid":166308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:51:33.000Z","msg":"軍政府<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國帶頭制裁未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb0e98357fa2cbbecb4b8c70139695d5195da42","tid":1900216,"uid":89857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"係極權架喇<br />\n但國際社會齋講<br />\n唔制裁香港又有咩用?"},{"pid":"3eb70781ed593de9aa327a112567f564494d722b","tid":1900216,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a80e8185524a22d4c10e5dcfbe72669ad0235cf","tid":1900216,"uid":166308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:51:33.000Z","msg":"軍政府<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國帶頭制裁未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"唔好因為肺炎而忘記我哋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b965b7c87c8b7ca5054ffd6d010dd8e6c23f7e41","tid":1900216,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfb0e98357fa2cbbecb4b8c70139695d5195da42","tid":1900216,"uid":89857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"係極權架喇<br />\n但國際社會齋講<br />\n唔制裁香港又有咩用?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:10:57.000Z","msg":"直情要武裝支援手足先至可以同三萬隻畜生抗衡"},{"pid":"2ab6b9b21331f33708814b6bae6e6b2cd2a3d185","tid":1900216,"uid":35438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e22ac3d6ad74ff99932365160591c73750eb44dc","tid":1900216,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:12:23.000Z","msg":"入境處處長係咪地下共產黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab5e7d49862aeed330b73377349c9c0860107b2","tid":1900216,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:13:44.000Z","msg":"肺炎患者禁左未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass